OL,3,CRiders from around the world take on
OL,4,CPenny Farthing Hill Climb in Eastbourne
OL,6,FWatch: ITV News Meridian's report is
OL,7,Fby Charlotte Wilkins
OL,9,F25 Penny Farthing riders have taken on
OL,10,Fthe 'gruelling' 3 mile hill climb from
OL,11,FEastbourne seafront to Beachy Head.
OL,13,FIn its 7th year, The World
OL,14,FChampionship Penny Farthing Hill Climb
OL,15,FTime Trial started off as a bit of a
OL,16,Fjoke as part of the Eastbourne Cycling
OL,17,FFestival when only 5 riders took part.
OL,19,FThis years event saw riders entering
OL,20,Ffrom all over the world and hundreds
OL,21,Flined the pavements to watch.
