OL,3,CRiders from around the world take on
OL,4,CPenny Farthing Hill Climb in Eastbourne
OL,6,FWatch: Ryan speaks to ITV Meridian.
OL,8,FDescribed by those who ride them as
OL,9,F'smile machines' Penny Farthings can
OL,10,Freach up to 30 miles an hour, but they
OL,11,Fhave a fixed gear and no brakes.
OL,13,FThe winners of this years time trial
OL,14,Fwere Charlie Burrell for the men and
OL,15,FMelissa Eisdell for the women.
